<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="N" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Narrowly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Narrowly,</orth> closely, with minute scrutiny: <cit><quote>if my cousin do not look exceeding n. to thee,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.4.118" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 4, 118</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>doth watch Bianca's steps so n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.141" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 141</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>search the market n.</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 2, 3</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>